Interface TupleSet<E>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SPCSet

    public interface TupleSet<E>
    Interface for sets, that consist of Tuples of Elements and behave like ArrayLists.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jan-Michael Holzinger
